article.headline: Portland St. 63, Texas Southern 55
article.story: HOUSTON -- Jamie Jones scored 13 points and had 10 rebounds to lead Portland State to a 63-55 victory over winless Texas Southern on Saturday night. Jeremiah Dominguez led the Vikings (9-3) with 15 points and Phil Nelson added 14. Deandre Hall scored 18 points and was the only player to reach double figures for Texas Southern (0-13).
